      "role": "user",
      "content": "but that's what everyone says. that it gets better. it doesn't feel like it's going to get better. it just feels like i'm a shell. i look in the mirror and i don't even recognize the person looking back. it’s like the real me died with him and i’m just… haunting this place. what is the point of just existing if none of the color is ever coming back?",
